fields.label: Config Type
fields.help_context: Enter a relevant Config type.

fields.label: Config Code
fields.help_context: The Config Code represents a value based on the selected type: if you select 'Region', enter the region code (e.g., IN-NORTH, US-EAST); if you select 'Header', enter a short text for the header (e.g., BR, PROP).

fields.label: Config Value
fields.help_context: The Config Value represents a name based on the selected type: if you select 'Region', enter the region name (e.g., ('California,New Mexico,.'); if you select 'Header', enter a name of the header.
